tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE clickstream_data (
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action VARCHAR,
    page_id INT,
    duration_sec INT
)

CREATE TABLE clickstream_data (
  event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_url VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE user_behavior (
  user_id INT,
  page_views INT,
  click_count INT,
  last_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE website_usability (
  page_url VARCHAR(255),
  avg_time_on_page FLOAT,
  bounce_rate FLOAT,
  unique_visitors INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (page_url)
);

CREATE TABLE WebClickstreamData (
    user_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    click_event VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE UserProfiles (
    user_id INT,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(50),
    age INT
)

CREATE TABLE PageDetails (
    page_id INT,
    page_title VARCHAR(100),
    page_url VARCHAR(200),
    category VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE UsersActivity (
    activity_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE web_clickstream_data ( 
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    user_id INT, 
    timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
    page_url VARCHAR(255), 
    referrer_url VARCHAR(255), 
    event_type VARCHAR(50) 
);

CREATE TABLE user_profile ( 
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    username VARCHAR(50), 
    email VARCHAR(100), 
    registration_date DATE, 
    last_login DATE 
);
